data.description: This home includes a beautiful kitchen with corian countertops, stainless steel appliances, dovetail cabinets and a wet bar/coffee bar. 1st floor laundry, a spacious bedroom & a half bath right off the 2 stall attached garage. There are 3 bedrooms & 2 bathooms on the 2nd story, and a bonus nonconforming 5th bedroom in the basement. Two glass doors in the great room open up to a beautiful 760sqft deck perfect for entertaining. Just over an acre of land that includes mature fruit trees, beautiful landscaping, and a 46 x 24 outbuilding that has a separate garage and work shop with outlets every 10ft, as well as, 220v for special shop equipment. New roof, new siding, and some new windows after derecho 2020. Highly desired Linn Mar schools & COUNTY TAXES. Schedule a private showing today!!
